id: pm-max1
title: Deduplicate recurrence weekday ordering helper
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: weekdayOrderIndex is repeated in four recurrence/calendar modules: src/core/item/item-format.ts:100, src/cli/commands/create.ts:510, src/cli/commands/update.ts:686, and src/cli/commands/calendar.ts:138. Each copy wraps RECURRENCE_WEEKDAY_VALUES.indexOf(value), making recurrence parsing/serialization/calendar expansion drift-prone. Existing recurrence implementation items are closed, and open pm-why9 covers create/update parser blocks but not the shared item-format/calendar weekday helper."
